Description: Full back up a web site + database where only cPanel access is available.

1) backup.sh - Goes on the remote server to run as a cronjob.
2) ftp.sh - Runs locally as a cronjob
3) netrc - Rename to .netrc and places within the home directory of the user that executes ftp.sh
4) delete.sh - Runs locally as a cronjob to remove files older than 14 days (or any other specified date)
